About me
Born and raised in Bogotá, Colombia with Chilean family from my mother's side.
Graduated from a double degree in Systems and Computer Engineering and Electronics Engineering at Universidad de los Andes (Bogotá, Colombia)
Due to the fact that I did an exchange semester in Lund, Sweden and an internship in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, I fell in love with working with people from all over the world.
Currently living and working in Santiago, Chile.
